{"ID":"20240513023814-b459osv","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"linux.png","id":"20240513023814-b459osv","title":"平板电脑安装Ubuntu教程","type":"doc","updated":"20240513023937"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240513023835-z8ob33c","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-z8ob33c","updated":"20240513023835"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyrme.lofter.com/post/418b24_94ce288#","TextMarkTextContent":"【轶哥博文】平板电脑安装Ubuntu教程-以V975w为例，Z3735系列CPU通用"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-8bub7xl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-8bub7xl","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最近尝试在昂达V975w平板电脑和intel stick中安装ubuntu，经过分析，发现存在一个非常大的坑。但因为这个坑，此教程适合大部分平板电脑、电脑棒、intel nuc设备安装Ubuntu。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-7dwxel2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-7dwxel2","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本教程适合以下读者："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-z61flix","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-z61flix","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、希望给自己的x86架构设备安装Ubuntu操作系统；"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-yflfa2d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-yflfa2d","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、希望使用32位的GRUB安装64位Ubuntu操作系统；"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-jdxdksv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-jdxdksv","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、想折腾Ubuntu系统在平板电脑或intel stick（intel电脑棒）中的使用；"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-oo2zm45","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-oo2zm45","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"本教程不适合以下读者："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-8xlc69i","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-8xlc69i","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、纯小白或纯粹不懂Linux命令的爱好者；"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-v9uxdi9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-v9uxdi9","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、没有折腾精神的人；"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-jvryotc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-jvryotc","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、非程序员爱好者。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-t5ctid7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-t5ctid7","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于部分平板电脑CPU不支持64位的GRUB引导程序，故而导致Ubuntu系统安装失败，而官网的Ubuntu系统只有64位支持UEFI引导。除了WIFI、蓝牙等驱动需要自己上网搜索安装之外，系统主要的安装和引导的具体方法如下："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-9ll9cvk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-9ll9cvk","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1、获取IOS镜像文件"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-hcgle09","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-hcgle09","updated":"20240513023937"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法一：如果你的CPU是Z3735D/F，那么下面这个IOS镜像直接拿去用吧（在官方的基础上增加了驱动，镜像来源："},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://www.linuxium.com.au","TextMarkTextContent":"www.linuxium.com.au"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"）："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-pndmbbo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-pndmbbo","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"链接: "},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1jGS9ux4","TextMarkTextContent":"http://pan.baidu.com/s/1jGS9ux4"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 密码: qbb6"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-undk18y","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-undk18y","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"方法二：如果你的CPU不支持64位引导程序，或者说你想自己手动修改官方的IOS镜像用于在平板电脑中安装系统，请到"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://www.ubuntu.com/","TextMarkTextContent":"官网"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下载镜像文件，需要注意，请勿下载国产修改版，不保证能够支持平板使用。请务必下载64位版本，32位不支持UEFI引导。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-ic2w3o1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-ic2w3o1","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"2、制作安装U盘"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-iwjofzf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-iwjofzf","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下载完成后下载U盘制作工具：'"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://rufus.akeo.ie/?locale=zh_CN","TextMarkTextContent":"Rufus"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"' on Windows or 'dd' on Linux"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-k6fg24n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-k6fg24n","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"制作一个UEFI引导的U盘。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-dalzueh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-dalzueh","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"3、修改UEFI引导文件"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-k34u7fv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-k34u7fv","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果使用方法一获取的IOS镜像文件，此步忽略。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-esiql3o","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-esiql3o","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下载"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/bootia32.efi_.zip","TextMarkTextContent":"bootia32.efi"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文件并解压复制到'EFI\\BOOT'目录下。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-ra2vap2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-ra2vap2","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"请先链接USB键鼠，使用快捷键进入BIOS（Z3735通常是DEL/ESC），修改BOOT顺序为UEFI引导的U盘。进入GRUE菜单后选择（Try Ubuntu With Install），如果之前配置的32位引导文件正确，此时你将直接进入Live CD模式的Ubuntu系统。在这个临时系统中的大部分操作都是无效的，不会被保存记录。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-g579h0v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-g579h0v","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"此时我们会看到桌面有安装Ubuntu操作系统的快捷方式，先别忙安装，看完这部分内容。点击左上角第一个应用（搜索），搜索\"Disks\"，进入硬盘管理软件，查看你的本地硬盘。特别提示，在平板电脑或intel stick等小型设备中，通常是SD卡模式，但绝非USB磁盘。通常显示在列表第一项。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-fyljk2a","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-fyljk2a","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"IMG8219"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8219-1024x768.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8219.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8219.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Ubuntu分区查看"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-iabhqs1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-iabhqs1","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由上图我们看到主硬盘所在路径为/dev/mmcblk0。由于我已经安装好了Ubuntu系统，所以看到其中有三个分区，第一个是存储EFI文件的FAT分区，第二个是存储文件的Ext4分区。如果你的平板设备还是win系统，这里应该是NTFS分区+FAT分区。这都不是重点，重点在于需要记录你的主硬盘所在路径“/dev/mmcblk0”还是“/dev/sda1”。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-1z6tryq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-1z6tryq","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"记录后点击桌面的快捷方式安装ubuntu到本地硬盘。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-ca6puyr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-ca6puyr","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"安装ubuntu"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8214-1024x768.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8214.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8214.jpg"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-9d7apbc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-9d7apbc","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"安装ubuntu过程"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8213-1024x768.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8213.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8213.jpg"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-0xzpd74","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-0xzpd74","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安装完毕进入下一步。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-jp4fg9v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-jp4fg9v","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"安装完毕重启我们将发现无法进入到操作系统，而是进入了EFI SHELL模式，早在意料之中，因为这类平板的CPU不支持64位的UEFI引导，但并不意味着不支持64位操作系统。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-sstn4u0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-sstn4u0","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"此时我们还是进入BIOS使用之前的U盘引导启动，进入GRUB菜单后不要选择，点击键盘中的\"c\"按钮，进入GRUB2命令行模式。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-aougx20","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-aougx20","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"进入该模式后，输入“ls”列出硬盘分区。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-lfxgklm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-lfxgklm","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"此时会看到类似(hd0,gtp1)或(hd1,msdos1)之类的项。这是你的硬盘分区。其中hd0为根目录所在的磁盘，IDE硬盘用hd开始，SCSI硬盘用sd开头。软盘用fd开头。命名和linux不大一样。是从0算起。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-2de0yyu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-2de0yyu","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们需要找出linux内核所在分区。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-5l3a6mh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-5l3a6mh","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用\"ls (hdX,gtpX)/boot\"，其中的“X”请手动替换为上一步出现过的数字，这里肯定要有逗号\",\"的，如果出现一大串结果，显示了你的linux内核文件，说明就是这个分区。记录X的值。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-lrapc4x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-lrapc4x","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假设你在执行\"ls (hd0,gtp2)/boot\"的时候出现值，那么下一步执行："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-kfredm3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-kfredm3","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"set root=(hd0,gtp2)"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-ggh7bfz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-ggh7bfz","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"然后输入需要输入内核路径，“linux /boot/vmlinuz* root=/dev/mmcblk0p2”其中*号为内核版本，输入/boot/vmlinuz后按tab键可以进行自动补全。mmcblk0p2为根目录所在的分区,其中“mmcblk0”是第二步查看分区记录的值，后面的\"p2\"是我猜的，你顺着p1\\p2\\p3猜测一下，能执行就对了。完整的命令例子如下："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-6ary7vb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-6ary7vb","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"linux (hd0,gpt2)/boot/vmlinuz-3.13-xxxx root=/dev/mmcblk0p5"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-3b0ugem","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-3b0ugem","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"initrd /initrd.img"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-3db9nyy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-3db9nyy","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"boot"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-wlvionq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-wlvionq","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"最后成功进入本地Ubuntu系统，这一步如果不成功的话就多尝试一下，修改上面涉及的各个值，祝你好运。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-u1xgulx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-u1xgulx","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"到这步已经成功了一半了，但是没人愿意每次启动都使用USB的GRUB引导并手动输入引导命令，这会很麻烦。进入本地Ubuntu后，调出终端，继续输入如下命令："}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-gp6d0wo","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-gp6d0wo","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"sudo apt-get update"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-z9f2ed9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-z9f2ed9","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"sudo apt-get -y purge grub-efi-amd64 grub-efi-amd64-bin grub-efi-amd64-signed"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-iqdihu1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-iqdihu1","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"sudo apt-get -y install grub-efi-ia32-bin grub-efi-ia32 grub-common grub2-common"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-z1jsifb","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-z1jsifb","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"sudo grub-install --target=i386-efi /dev/mmcblk0p2 --efi-directory=/boot/efi/ --boot-directory=/boot/ 【这里的“mmcblk0p2 ”就是上一步你执行成功的那个值】"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-nzszuhm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-nzszuhm","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"sudo grub-mkconfig -o /boot/grub/grub.cfg"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-ir2zf8n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-ir2zf8n","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"最后一步"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8216-1024x768.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8216.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8216.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"执行完毕后重启，发现Ubuntu引导正常，不需要USB引导也可以进入系统。恭喜！安装成功！"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-myh5267","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-myh5267","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"安装Ubuntu成功"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8217-1024x768.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8217.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8217.jpg"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-qw680ht","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-qw680ht","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"当然了，执行第四步的前提条件是连接了网络，这里需要先安装好网络相关的驱动。如果遇到问题，可以给我留言，我会帮助你的。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-etys7rc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-etys7rc","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"高分屏幕在win下很鸡肋，因为windows对高分辨显示屏的支持是在太差了。而Ubuntu不同，使用Ubuntu的显示设置可以像Mac一样进行缩放，有类似Ritina的显示效果，执行各种命令管理远程Linux服务器很赞。"}]},{"ID":"20240513023835-aec5vqn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513023835-aec5vqn","updated":"20240513023836"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​"},{"Type":"NodeImage","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang"},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket"},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"使用Ubuntu"},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket"},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen"},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8218-e1450366132111-768x1024.jpg"},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen"}]},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8218.jpg","TextMarkTextContent":"http://wyr.me/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/IMG_8218.jpg"}]}]}